
################################################################################
                      Assassin guild news (Yeah!)

Ok, guild quests are in place.  There are three of them.  Have fun!

Yes, I gave in to all you weasels and made a corpse healing thingy.
'cann(ibalize)' will let you eat those poor corpses.

If you are paralyzed by the vampire guild spell 'paralyze',
you can release yourself by the ability, 'unpara'.

Things to come:
Lots of neat poisons for assassins to use.

New command: pkers -- shows list of pkers logged on.
ac now supports emoting using the ':' convention.

################################################################################

